00:03:25,024 --> 00:03:27,224
Itu mustahil, Tn. Detektif.

33
00:03:28,224 --> 00:03:31,923
Karena dalam kisah ini...

34
00:03:31,924 --> 00:03:35,423
Hanya ada si aktris janda itu, putrinya si tikus,

35
00:03:35,424 --> 00:03:37,224
